      "line": 218,
      "message": "This is not used here, since at this point, the class level `endTime` field that is checked in the method is not null:\n```java\nif (endTime != null) {\n    return endTime;\n}\n\nString endTs = params.getFirst(\"endTs\");\n```\nTherefore it does not reach `params.getFirst(\"endTs\")` and the stub is not used.\nLikely you can fix this be re-instantiating the object under test, that you don't have that state here",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 7849,
        "name": "Fiete Ostkamp",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de",
